Installation
============

Command: bundle install

Bundle will install "rspec" dependencies


Tests
=====

Command: "rspec"


Execute program
===============

From root directory: irb

irb-session> require './lib/interpreter.rb'

=> true

irb-session>Interpreter.new { who("David").feel("awesome") }.output


Notes
=====

The file "dictionary.csv" inside the root directory lets you add new domain
specific "commands". Structure of the file:
<verb_key>,<verb_inside_the_sentence>,<sentence>

<SUBJECT>, <VERB> and <PREDICATE> are reserved word

IMPORTANT: The order of the rows inside the file defines the order the verbs
are managed by the interpreter.
